class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黎緊有2個miss唔教了，果2個都好既，其餘淨翻落黎果d就&hellip;&hellip;只可以話冇heart囉，為錢教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n簡單講就係你係讀書好叻既，咁就應該得心應手啦，但如果好似我咁讀書唔太叻一心為廚藝而翻，就要有心理準備加把勁同犧牲多d私人時間黎做功課&amp;溫書啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左基本既英文，普通話，烹飪課之外仲有Accounting, Management ,Menu planning, Nutrition, Culture ,Wine   etc&hellip;<br />\n講咁多野唔係想打沉你，只係想你有個心理準備姐，唔好諗得太輕鬆囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：我係你岩上year 2既師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"564a2efb44c0a5c79843ae5ef530d2910e18ae6f","tid":318518,"uid":115701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:20:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>[img]<a href=\"https://holland.pk/x2zys5iq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fx2zys5iq&d=zGtP91e91EobyQ7eT8PbaKMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=8e6b18c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://holland.pk/x2zys5iq</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係因為覺得中餐多野玩過西餐 巴打點解想揀翻中</blockquote><br />\n中餐又唔會多野玩過西餐既，我想揀翻中就係因為西太多野玩，由朝早8點翻到夜晚830，仲要N咁多projects,人都癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，中餐D上課時間相對輕鬆好多。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打讀hd?</blockquote><br />\n冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />讀hd係錯撚曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解hd錯撚晒 我係想以煮野食為興趣學 有咩途徑入學</blockquote><br />\n為興趣可以報翻最普通果隻 <br />\n最起碼唔洗日日上堂 <br />\n一開始同中後期上 其他都係實戰多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前見hd果啲 唔係上堂就係睇我地出餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n衣家都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d90b1a0e3ab8bca69b9b7fde38c73cde56f89dc","ti