iploma上佢個網睇翻邊到近你地點報名<br />\n<br />\n基本上你有錢就讀得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ea80396dac66fddad6b103fea3f79ac1cc5becb","tid":318518,"uid":47747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T03:37:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>[img]<a href=\"https://holland.pk/x2zys5iq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fx2zys5iq&d=zGtP91e91EobyQ7eT8PbaKMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=8e6b18c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://holland.pk/x2zys5iq</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係因為覺得中餐多野玩過西餐 巴打點解想揀翻中</blockquote><br />\n中餐又唔會多野玩過西餐既，我想揀翻中就係因為西太多野玩，由朝早8點翻到夜晚830，仲要N咁多projects,人都癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，中餐D上課時間相對輕鬆好多。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打讀hd?</blockquote><br />\n冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />讀hd係錯撚曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解既？今年準備讀year1 有冇多d野聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來你已經半隻腳叉左入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁講學唔學到野就實學到既，只不過濕尻既只係佢d制度，year 1頭2個sem係開心既，頭2個sem係要中西廚都學既，但上課時間唔算長，冇乜壓力，一到year 2，差不多第三個sem揀完中or西廚既時候就黎料，例如上堂時間on9啦，朝8晚830，有d科目仲要100%attendance，每個星期都有projects,有d老師冇乜料到啦，p.s我本人另外有份pt係做廚師既，同多國廚師合作過，所以都識分邊d係有料既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黎緊有2個miss唔教了，果2個都好既，其餘淨翻落黎果d就&hellip;&hellip;只可以話冇heart囉，為錢教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n簡單講就係你係讀書好叻既，咁就應該得心應手啦，但如果好似我咁讀書唔太叻一心為廚藝而翻，就要有心理準備加把勁同犧牲多d私人時間黎做功課&amp;溫書啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左基本既英文，普通話，烹飪課之外仲有Accounting, Management ,Menu planning, Nutrition, Culture ,Wine   etc&hellip;<br />\n講咁多野唔係想打沉你，只係想你有個心理準備姐，唔好諗得太輕鬆囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：我係你岩上year 2既師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比你咁樣講一講都唔知自己應唔應付到，小弟係fd升上黎，讀係因為為興趣同想拎張hd 既cert 咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3656d945c1b18b8704a97580574d28079cf317f","tid":318518,"uid":117237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:11:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解hd錯撚晒 我係想以煮野食為興趣學 有咩途徑入學</blockquote><br />\n為興趣可以報翻最普通果隻 <br />\n最起碼唔洗日日上堂 <br />\n一開始同中後期上 其他都係實戰多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前見hd果啲 唔係上堂就係睇我地出餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最普通個隻係咪就咁報名畀錢都有得學</blockquote><br />\n點報名我就唔知啦，btw，我知報親興趣班果d大部份都好有料到，佢地好多都係出面酒樓大廚想升職而黎讀個雞精course拎張cert，佢地拋鑊拋到9樓咁高，老師教既野佢合埋對眼都識整，你報果d既話都係純粹去睇佢地表演<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n西廚有冇好介紹</blockquote><br />\n你可以試下讀一般既diploma 囉，多好多烹飪堂，HD就theory 為主，適合d想要埋張HD cert，有心讀書既人讀，為興趣就唔好揀HD啦，揀DIPLOMA 啦~<br />\nBTW&hellip;&hellip;HD先有囡，我果年就一半男一半女，今年year 1就大部份女，diploma會dry D既，你諗你啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我溝女唔駛上興趣班<br />\n直接落club 啦<br />\n<br />\n係想學下基本功同興趣"},{"pid":"5ac7155e02298358cd8632b2cbe720ca61ba70a6","tid":318518,"uid":117237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:17:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n為興趣可以報翻最普通果隻 <br />\n最起碼唔洗日日上堂 <br />\n一開始同中後期上 其他都係實戰多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></